Pseudocode:

The Scenario: Several. Tell them of different ways that they can help.

START OF PROGRAM
	Tell user how the world is bad.
	Tell user that they might be able to try and make parts of it better.
	Let user choose from a list of methods to try to make the world a better place.
	Once a method is chosen, explain that method.
	Ask if user wants to see the other methods.
	If yes, go back to the list.
	If no, bid them farewell.
END OF PROGRAM
